title: Cocky Origins
description: Librarian Note: Retitled alternate cover editions of ASIN B07YTHSS3B can be found here and here True Love ... where the Cocker Family began.Jerald Daniel Cocker, a submarine planesman for the Navy on special leave in Georgia, USA, meets the girl we now know as "Grams" at the end of World War II.
author: Faleena Hopkins
